{"tid":355326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙南部度假海灘驚現一群北非難民乘橡皮艇搶『上岸 』","createTime":"2017-08-11T08:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T05:40:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a12122f67381c70b590541a5070952592164ddb","tid":355326,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSmlyEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSmlyEy.jpg&h=ca21da4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一批北非難民如大軍壓境乘坐一艘橡皮艇，成功飄流到西班牙南部度假海灘。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpM4PcFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpM4PcFf.jpg&h=abf8c705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">在船隻靠近較淺的海岸後，就有難民迫不及待跳入海水並往岸上奔跑。難民們在上岸後更隨即鳥獸散，讓一群遊客看得目瞪口呆。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一群北非難民昨（9）日乘坐一艘橡皮艇，成功飄流到西班牙南部度假海灘，嚇壞正在沙灘度假的民眾；警方獲報後隨即趕赴現場，但大批難民早已在警方到場前散去。西班牙休達市的政府代表尼古拉斯則痛斥邊界安全撤底失敗。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，大約20幾名難民擠在一艘小小的橡皮艇上，於9日下午漂流到西班牙西南部的卡迪斯沙灘，在船隻靠近較淺的海岸後，就有難民迫不及待跳入海中並往岸上奔跑。<br />\n<br />\n難民們在上岸後更隨即鳥獸散，讓一群遊客看得目瞪口呆。一名在沙灘度假的男子剛好將畫面拍下，從影片中可聽到，嚇壞的遊客驚訝地問說「發生了什麼事？」<br />\n<br />\n警方趕到場時，已看不到任何非法入境的難民，西班牙當局為此宣布關閉休達市（Ceuta）邊境，市政府代表尼古拉斯（Nicol&aacute;s Fern&aacute;ndez Cucurull）也痛批，移民中心沒做好邊境安全。不過移民中心發言人反駁，指此問題應歸咎於歐盟，因為休達位於申根地區之外，未受歐盟重視；移民中心說，他們無法解決這項問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DpgbOUKAcSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDpgbOUKAcSg&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=a8bfd3b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DpgbOUKAcSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2159302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2159302&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=a69b83c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2159302&h=6c10d7b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2159302</a>"},{"pid":"bbd61ddb124d72c47447a0a096ff98f72bbac68c","tid":355326,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"好撚壯觀"},{"pid":"3cc6a54cee6877f81b3f3dead64f94d78aac8185","tid":355326,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"搶灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a81f7ddc03d1072009a56dc37d9d8fb1604feb0","tid":355326,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"國防廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05239cb27bddcd88dfeb86640811a135fb52e196","tid":355326,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"黑潮"},{"pid":"576aa21451503932fac259da267aa71b9d8dd661","tid":355326,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"摩洛哥同西班牙真係好近<br />\n唔計ceuta，去西班牙搭船一個鐘就到<br />\n<br />\n係摩洛哥邊境過去ceuta超輕鬆，上個月過完<br />\n即日來回西班牙"},{"pid":"ef839893fc679bea300100246d7cfcb5ca916a67","tid":355326,"uid":41602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"香港日日都150啦<br />\n<br />\n大驚少怪"},{"pid":"468ac4b9bcdb20756f013a4f45ac23c263dce92b","tid":355326,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩洛哥同西班牙真係好近<br />\n唔計ceuta，去西班牙搭船一個鐘就到<br />\n<br />\n係摩洛哥邊境過去ceuta超輕鬆，上個月過完<br />\n即日來回西班牙</blockquote><br />\n休達本來就位於非洲<br />\n唔係西班牙本土"},{"pid":"c3a279fe7789d1382c06ddede6adf0412ca15c11","tid":355326,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":